OL,3,CRecycling firm fined #2m after worker
OL,4,Chit and crushed by shovel loader
OL,6,FA recycling company has been fined
OL,7,Fmore than #2m after a picking
OL,8,Foperative worker was crushed under the
OL,9,Fwheels of an 18-tonne shovel loader.
OL,11,FAgency worker Dean Atkinson, 35, was
OL,12,Fkilled instantly when the truck hit
OL,13,Fand drove over him as he was returning
OL,14,Fto his workstation from a toilet break
OL,15,Fthree years ago on Tuesday (30
OL,16,FJanuary).
