OL,6,FThere was also no health and safety
OL,7,Fofficer employed at the Hartlepool
OL,8,Ffacility.
OL,10,FThe court heard that Ward Recycling
OL,11,Fopened in 2019 at a cost of #7m.
OL,12,FTeesside Crown Court was told the
OL,13,Fowner of Ward Recycling, Michael Ward,
OL,14,F55, also owned the recruitment agency
OL,15,Finvolved which took on Mr Atkinson.
OL,17,FMr Atkinson was working on a line
OL,18,Fwhich separated cardboard from paper
OL,19,Fand waste paper.
