OL,6,FThe court heard that Ward's other
OL,7,Frecycling plant, in Middlesbrough, had
OL,8,Fbeen issued with a notice of
OL,9,Fcontravention in 2018, by the HSE,
OL,10,Fbecause there was "no traffic plan".
OL,12,FA statement from Mr Atkinson's fiance,
OL,13,FJeanette Magson, read out in court
OL,14,Fsaid the pair had been together for 16
OL,15,Fyears and had a "very happy
OL,16,Frelationship".
