OL,6,FShe added: "Dean was such a lovely
OL,7,Fstep-dad to the children. He had
OL,8,Fbecome a grandad too." Ms Magson said
OL,9,Fher partner should have had the rest
OL,10,Fof his life to look forward to.
OL,12,FWard Recycling was fined #2.15m and
OL,13,Fgiven three months to pay. The fine
OL,14,Fwas made up of #1.75 million for
OL,15,Fcorporate manslaughter and #400,000
OL,16,Ffor breaching health and safety
OL,17,Fregulations.
