OL,6,FThe judge acknowledged that the fine
OL,7,F"is unlikely" to ever be paid because
OL,8,Fthe company has gone into liquidation,
OL,9,Fand owes creditors money. But Judge
OL,10,FWatson said the fine would "act as a
OL,11,Fdeterrent" to other companies.
OL,13,FAfter the sentencing, HSE Inspector
OL,14,FStephen Garner said: "This tragic
OL,15,Fincident could easily have been
OL,16,Favoided if Ward Recycling had
OL,17,Fimplemented simple control measures.
OL,18,FFollowing the incident, it took the
OL,19,Fcompany less than a week to put in
OL,20,Fplace an alternative traffic route to
OL,21,Fprotect pedestrians.
